data.description: Large family home with 5/6 bedrooms & 3 full baths. You enter through an elegant entry with the home office on one side & the secondary bedroom & full bath on the other. As you continue to the family room you will pass the stairway up & the formal dining room. The large family room includes a fireplace with gas connection & a large window overlooking the spacious fenced back yard. The open concept includes the family room/breakfast area/kitchen with long breakfast bar as a divider. Included with the home is the kitchen refrigerator & washer/dryer. The master bedroom with ensuite bath includes a jetted tub & separate stall shower with double sinks. Upstairs is the spacious game room with pool table included, surrounded by 3 bedrooms with walk in closets & a separate sitting area & full bath. This home has the perfect accommodations for your whole family. THIS HOME HAS NEVER FLOODED.
